{
  "stem": "20405.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Carol, can I get up?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not Italians.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Greeks.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was not only me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took away all-- the most Italian citizens born in Greece.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they put 'em in a kind of a ghetto, call him, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No, they took us first, I remember, in a big building which was from a tobacco company, right on the rooftop.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then when the Italian came and start to bombard over there with the airplanes, they took us away from there because it was very dangerous.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they took us to another Italian school we had right by the ocean over there, which, over there, we got bombarded with the first day we were there.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But nobody was hurt, anyway.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And from there, in maybe in three or four days, they took us away from there and then they got us in Peloponnese, call him, which is at the end of Greece.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they put over there-- they put us over there in a-- in a soldier's camp, military camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then, because we had with us too many Italian citizens, Jewish, very rich-- was not only the Jewish, was case [INAUDIBLE] with us, all the Italians, they start to complain about it-- food, and for the beds, because they were very good-- very rich people.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they start to complain to the English Embassy, just to take us away from there because we're born in Greece.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "At least, to take off the Jewish only from there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Which they did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they took us near Athens, to a very nice hotel.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And all those rich people paying for our food and everything else from the restaurants around.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Then, over there, we got liberated from the Germans.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
